import React from 'react'
import { Card, CardHeader, CardBody, Box, Collapsible, Grommet } from 'grommet'

export default function ContactCard(props) {
    return (
        <Grommet>
            <Collapsible flex direction='horizontal'>
                <Card height={'small'} width={'medium'} background={'light-1'} align='center'>
                    <CardHeader pad="xxsmall">{props.name}</CardHeader>
                    <CardBody pad="xxsmall">
                        <Box direction='column' justify='around'>
                            <Box>{props.phone}</Box>
                            <Box>{props.email}</Box>
                        </Box>
                    </CardBody>
                </Card >
            </Collapsible>
        </Grommet>
    )
}
